column2: SELECT 	s.specObjID ,	s.bestObjID ,	s.survey ,	s.instrument ,	s.programname ,	s.spectrographID ,	s.fiberID ,	s.legacy_target1 ,	CASE (s.legacy_target1 & #) WHEN # THEN # ELSE # END AS fLRG ,	s.special_target1 ,	CASE (s.special_target1 & #) | (s.special_target1 & #) WHEN # THEN # ELSE # END AS fDeepLRG ,	CASE (s.special_target1 & #) WHEN # THEN # ELSE # END AS fBCG  ,	s.boss_target1 ,	s.ancillary_target1 ,	CASE (s.ancillary_target1 & #) WHEN # THEN # ELSE # END AS fBRIGHTGAL ,	s.ancillary_target2 ,	s.primTarget ,	CASE (s.primTarget & #) WHEN # THEN # ELSE # END AS fLRGpT ,	s.sourceType ,	s.targetType ,	s.ra ,	s.dec ,	s.blueFiber ,	s.z, s.zErr, s.zWarning ,	s.class, s.subClass ,	s.z_noqso, s.zErr_noqso, s.zWarning_noqso ,	s.class_noqso, s.subClass_noqso ,	s.velDisp, s.velDispErr into mydb.SpecObj1 from SpecObj	s 	JOIN Galaxy g ON g.SpecObjID = s.SpecObjID
